p(x) = x^k
x^k = x_1^{k_1}\cdots x_n^{k_n}
\binom{k}{j} = \binom{k_1}{j_1} \cdots \binom{k_n}{j_n}
(p \ast g)(x) = \int (x-t)^k dg(t) = \sum_{j \le k } \binom{k}{j} x^j \int (-t)^{k-j} dg(t)
